ArivoFinance is **Ariverse Studio's** flagship in-house SaaS product — a comprehensive Financial ERP (Enterprise Resource Planning) platform built specifically for Indonesian SMEs and startups. It integrates invoicing, accounting, tax management, and project tracking into one seamless, secure, and automated ecosystem.

---

## Key Features

- **End-to-End Financial Suite** — Automated modules for invoicing & quotations, expense tracking, and professional accounting (P&L, Balance Sheets) adhering to Indonesian **PSAK** and **DJP** standards.
- **Project-Based Financial Tracking** — Integrated project management that monitors budgets, team progress, and real-time profitability from a unified dashboard.
- **Seamless Fintech Integration** — Built-in connectivity with major payment gateways and banks (Stripe, Midtrans, Xendit, BCA, Mandiri, PayPal) for automated payment reminders and reconciliations.
- **Enterprise-Grade Security** — End-to-end data encryption, multi-tenant Row Level Security (RLS), and a comprehensive audit trail monitoring every critical action.
- **Dynamic UX/UI Dashboard** — A high-performance admin interface featuring real-time cash flow analytics, revenue trends, and operational insights — designed for speed and clarity.
- **Scalable Subscription Engine** — Multi-tier pricing architecture (Free, Pro, Enterprise) with automated billing and member management.

---

## Scale & Impact

- **2,500+ active businesses** on the platform
- Processes transactions worth **trillions of IDR** annually
- Serving clients across multiple industries in Indonesia

---

## Tech Stack

Built with **Next.js**, Supabase (multi-tenant RLS), and integrated with major Indonesian and global payment infrastructure.

---

## Our Contribution

> *"ArivoFinance is our North Star — the most technically complex product we've shipped. Building a financial platform that's both powerful enough for enterprise clients and approachable enough for a small warung owner is an ongoing design and engineering challenge we embrace."*

As an in-house product, ArivoFinance is the clearest proof of **Ariverse Studio's** peak capability in high-availability SaaS infrastructure, complex financial logic, and professional-grade software development.
